<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1662,1941]" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,407,1734,1760]" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">Taxonomic notes:</emphasis>
It was described on a single male specimen, being compared with 
<taxonomicName authority="Treitschke, 1825" authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1934" box="[1140,1270,1734,1760]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Bryophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="barbaria">
<emphasis box="[1140,1270,1734,1760]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. barbaria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Treitschke, 1825" authorityName="Treitschke" authorityYear="1825" baseAuthorityName="Boursin" baseAuthorityYear="1954" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Bryophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="blepharista">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. blepharista</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, in a text where 
<taxonomicName authority="Treitschke, 1825" authorityName="Treitschke" authorityYear="1825" baseAuthorityName="Forster" baseAuthorityYear="1771" box="[394,512,1770,1796]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Bryophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="muralis">
<emphasis box="[394,512,1770,1796]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. muralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Treitschke, 1825" authorityName="Treitschke" authorityYear="1825" baseAuthorityName="Corley" baseAuthorityYear="2015" box="[568,714,1770,1796]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Bryophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="domestica">
<emphasis box="[568,714,1770,1796]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. domestica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were also mentioned as similar taxa. 
<bibRefCitation author="Boursin, C." box="[1142,1313,1770,1797]" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" pagination="85 - 89" refId="ref7601" refString="Boursin, C. (1954) Zwei neue Cryphia Hb. (Bryophila) - Arten aus dem vorderasiatisch-mediterranean Faunenkreis. (Beitrage zur Kenntnis der &quot; Agrotidae-Trifinae &quot; 66). Zeitschrift der Wiener Entomologischen Gesellschaft, 39, 85 - 89." type="journal article" year="1954">Boursin (1954)</bibRefCitation>
stated that this species and 
<taxonomicName authority="Treitschke, 1825" authorityName="Treitschke" authorityYear="1825" baseAuthorityName="Boursin" baseAuthorityYear="1954" box="[340,501,1806,1832]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Bryophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="blepharista">
<emphasis box="[340,501,1806,1832]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. blepharista</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are very similar externally but 
<taxonomicName authority="Treitschke, 1825" authorityName="Treitschke" authorityYear="1825" baseAuthorityName="Boursin" baseAuthorityYear="1954" box="[863,1095,1806,1832]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Bryophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="schwingenschussi">
<emphasis box="[863,1095,1806,1832]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. schwingenschussi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has shorter pectination of the male antennae, slenderer uncus, somewhat longer valvae and the vesica is armed with a strong cornutus which is missing from both 
<taxonomicName authority="Treitschke, 1825" authorityName="Treitschke" authorityYear="1825" baseAuthorityName="Boursin" baseAuthorityYear="1954" box="[364,523,1878,1904]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Bryophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="blepharista">
<emphasis box="[364,523,1878,1904]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. blepharista</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Treitschke, 1825" authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1934" box="[577,708,1878,1904]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Bryophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="barbaria">
<emphasis box="[577,708,1878,1904]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. barbaria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. As far as is known, it is restricted to 
<collectingCountry box="[1130,1235,1879,1905]" name="Morocco" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">Morocco</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
